@startuml
skinparam titleFontSize 24
skinparam titleFontStyle bold
title Service Booking Process (Reservation Subsystem)

|Customer|
start
:Access Booking Page;
:View Available Services;

|System|
:Load Active Services;
:Display Service Catalog;

|Customer|
:Select Service/Service Package;

|System|
:Calculate Service Duration;
:Check Bay Availability;
:Display Available Time Slots;

|Customer|
:Select Preferred Date & Time;

|System|
:Validate Slot Availability;

if (Time Slot Available?) then (Yes)
  :Reserve Time Slot Temporarily;

  |Customer|
  :Review Booking Details;
  :Confirm Booking;

  |System|
  :Create Service Order Record;
  :Assign Bay (if available);
  :Calculate Estimated Wait Time;
  :Save to Database;

  |Admin|
  :Receive New Booking Notification;
  :Review Booking Queue;
  :Organize Customer Confirmation;
  :Optimize Bay Assignment;

  |System|
  fork
    :Send Confirmation Email to Customer;
  fork again
    :Send SMS Notification;
  end fork

  :Display Success Message;
  :Show Booking Reference Number;

  |Customer|
  :Receive Confirmation;
  :View Real-Time Wait Time;

else (No)
  :Display "Slot Unavailable" Message;
  :Suggest Alternative Time Slots;
  |Customer|
  :Select Different Time Slot;
endif

stop
@enduml
